div.p:
In <email> and <webpage>, it is recommended to include the
                            email address or URL twice, both as text and as value of the attribute
                            @href, for a better use in browsers.

attDef.desc:
Name of the country the repository is located in encoded
                                    according to ISO 3166-1, e.g. "DE" for "Germany", "GB" for
                                    "Great Britain and Northern Ireland", "FR" for "France";
                                    mandatory;
